title: 848. Deshaun Watson's Suspension & Pivotal Rookies with Lance Zierlein
itunes:title: 848. Deshaun Watson's Suspension & Pivotal Rookies with Lance Zierlein
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks and is joined by NFL Media's Lance Zierlein. To start off, the guys react to the news of the NFL and NFLPA agreeing to an 11-game suspension and $5 million fine for Browns quarterback Deshaun Watson. Then for the rest of the show, Lance goes through his pivotal rookies for each division.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
